frames.caption: A miniature train travels through a tunnel formed by large, overlapping cabbage leaves. Tiny figures stand on a wooden platform beside the tracks, observing the train's journey through this whimsical, leafy landscape.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical setting where a small train navigates through a tunnel created by giant cabbage leaves. The environment is lush and green, with a sense of wonder and imagination.

frames.caption: A miniature blue train chugs along a track surrounded by lush green cabbage leaves. The train emits gentle puffs of steam as it navigates through the verdant tunnel. The scene captures a whimsical blend of nature and miniature engineering.
frames.description: The scene depicts a small, detailed model train traveling through a tunnel formed by large cabbage leaves. The setting is imaginative, combining elements of nature with a playful, miniature world.
